like":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddc51921ab98185705cc855251b6360e07c3faf7","tid":1700570,"uid":56954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bd4eedc353d5df12ca497881cfe7e4c9aa9a16a","tid":1700570,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7bf01e4c32c42bb9f63993cb2ee00b0da3f2ce1","tid":1700570,"uid":56954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T16:43:21.000Z","msg":"但搞紅官阻嚇性&gt;法庭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T16:52:26.000Z","msg":"搞紅官畫面咪仲難睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T16:57:24.000Z","msg":"咁講真搞法院都唔好睇得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好易比對方入藐視法律<br />\n仲要大量文宣都未必救到<br />\n未計而加貼文宣風險比以前高同小左人貼<br />\n可以話係贏面低既方式<br />\n但搞紅官可以暗底啞做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T07:26:06.000Z","msg":"又係唔好激嬲中共/港共系列<br />\n畫面唔靚/俾位人入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f15d91993e17961caec1f18573a09f083b0b7d4a","tid":1700570,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T07:41:51.000Z","msg":"做文宣先 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「人民不應該害怕他們的政府，政府應該害怕它的人民。」（People should not be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.）<br />\n<br />\n「藝術家用謊言揭露真相，政治家用謊言掩蓋真相。」（Artists use lies to tell the truth, while politicians use them to cover the truth up.）<br />\n<br />\n「沒有舞蹈的革命，是不值得發動的革命。」（A revolution without dancing is a revolution not worth having）<br />\n<br />\n「面具之下只是個血肉之軀，而在這面具之下的，還有一個理念，只不過，理念，是刀槍不入的。」（Beneath this mask there is more than flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea, Mr.Creedy, and ideas are bulletproof..）<br />\n<br />\n「我們的尊嚴可能不值錢，但它卻是我們唯一真正擁有的東西。它是我們最後一寸領地，但在那一寸領地裡，我們是自由的。」（Our integrity sells for so little, but it is all we really have. It is the very last inch of us, but within that inch, we are free）<br />\n<br />\n「力量來自團結，團結來自信念」（Strength through unity, unity through faith）<br />\n<br />\n「恐懼往往是政府的終極武器。」（Fear became the ultimate tool of this government）<br />\n<br />\n「就算政府擁有的武力統治不讓人民發言，自由的言論仍然充滿著強大的力量。」（the truncheon may be used in lieu of conversation, words will always retain their power)"},{"pid":"b75ecc15aa23934e104f32d5e309fca5ba68a6f7","tid":1700570,"uid":56954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58d95453fe626d80ef260b922c3010067502b403","tid":1700570,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddc51921ab98185705cc855251b6360e07c3faf7","tid":1700570,"uid":56954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bd4eedc353d5df12ca497881cfe7e4c9aa9a16a","tid":1700570,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T16:52:26.000Z","msg":"搞紅官畫面咪仲難睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T16:57:24.000Z","msg":"咁講真搞法院都唔好睇得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好易比對方入藐視法律<br />\n仲要大量文宣都未必救到<br />\n未計而加貼文宣風險比以前高同小左人貼<br />\n可以話係贏面低既方式<br />\n但搞紅官可以暗底啞做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T07:26:06.000Z","msg":"又係唔好激嬲中共/港共系列<br />\n畫面唔靚/俾位人入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T09:55:15.000Z","msg":"你咁講不如見親中賣港人士就殺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊個賣港就殺邊個 乜撚都唔駛理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da1804ff633e438938716248124c1cb0c2f5c8cc","tid":1700570,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eeb46cb8585cd93d6f98c859bdf11d46c554ebbd","tid":1700570,"uid":46042,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T14:58:54.000Z","msg":"2015:唔好搞升旗 會落中央面"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T10:10:23.000Z","msg":"黃之鋒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ac11322fa70e48929c0e01a3df90b2ffe2ecca","tid":1700570,"uid":310883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T10:13:38.000Z","msg":"一個係立法機關